Package: rNeighborLMM
Title: Fitting mixed models for oligogenic and polygenic indirect genetic effects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Yasuhiro", family = "Sato", email = "sato.yasuhiro.36c@kyoto-u.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6466-723X")),person(given = "Kosuke", family = "Hamazaki", role = "aut"))
Description: This package serves as a wrapper of RAINBOWR and rNeighborGWAS, which solves a multi-kernel mixed model incorporating direct and indirect genetic effects with their covariance. GWAS of oligogenic indirect genetic effects can be performed following the same way as rNeighborGWAS operates. See Sato & Hamazaki (2026) for theoretical details.
